name: Bryan Alex
description: Here’s a little about me………. I’m a nice, honest and understanding person.. With a great sense of humor..always optimistic, creative, down to earth, and easy going, With lots lots of love and care inside to share with the right person… I enjoy hanging out with the people I love and care about. Family and friends are a very important part of my life. I enjoy doing the usual stuff u know, goin out chillin with family and friends all that good stuff. I always try to keep my life exciting and interesting. I treasure each and every friendship like the most precious thing in the world……… To my friends and family, I am extremely loving, caring and very considerate.
